Suggests: xfonts-100dpi | xfonts-75dpi, xfonts-scalable
Maintainer: enveezee <enveezee@gmail.com>
Description: Headless Xorg server optimized for Sunshine streaming
 This package provides a minimal, headless Xorg build intended for
 GPU-accelerated game streaming via Sunshine. It disables logind,
 suid, Xwayland, nested servers, and other desktop-oriented features.